{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-post-js","path":"/Algorithm/Programmers/프로그래머스 - 전화번호 목록(Hash Lv.2)/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"춤추는 기술 블로그","comment":{"utterances":"ensia96/ensia96.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"ensia96"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"be701343-0534-53fe-93ba-a978def53b57","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/Algorithm/Programmers/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%A8%B8%EC%8A%A4%20-%20%EC%A0%84%ED%99%94%EB%B2%88%ED%98%B8%20%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D(Hash%20Lv.2)/#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\">문제 확인</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Algorithm/Programmers/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%A8%B8%EC%8A%A4%20-%20%EC%A0%84%ED%99%94%EB%B2%88%ED%98%B8%20%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D(Hash%20Lv.2)/#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85\">문제 설명</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Algorithm/Programmers/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%A8%B8%EC%8A%A4%20-%20%EC%A0%84%ED%99%94%EB%B2%88%ED%98%B8%20%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D(Hash%20Lv.2)/#%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%9C-%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\">제한 사항</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Algorithm/Programmers/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%A8%B8%EC%8A%A4%20-%20%EC%A0%84%ED%99%94%EB%B2%88%ED%98%B8%20%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D(Hash%20Lv.2)/#%EC%9E%85%EC%B6%9C%EB%A0%A5-%EC%98%88%EC%A0%9C\">입출력 예제</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Algorithm/Programmers/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%A8%B8%EC%8A%A4%20-%20%EC%A0%84%ED%99%94%EB%B2%88%ED%98%B8%20%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D(Hash%20Lv.2)/#%EC%9E%85%EC%B6%9C%EB%A0%A5-%EC%98%88-%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85\">입출력 예 설명</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Algorithm/Programmers/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%A8%B8%EC%8A%A4%20-%20%EC%A0%84%ED%99%94%EB%B2%88%ED%98%B8%20%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D(Hash%20Lv.2)/#%EC%A0%9C%EA%B3%B5%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%86%8C%EC%8A%A4-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C\">제공하는 소스 코드</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Algorithm/Programmers/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%A8%B8%EC%8A%A4%20-%20%EC%A0%84%ED%99%94%EB%B2%88%ED%98%B8%20%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D(Hash%20Lv.2)/#%EC%A0%91%EA%B7%BC\">접근</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Algorithm/Programmers/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%A8%B8%EC%8A%A4%20-%20%EC%A0%84%ED%99%94%EB%B2%88%ED%98%B8%20%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D(Hash%20Lv.2)/#%EA%B2%80%EC%83%89\">검색</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Algorithm/Programmers/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%A8%B8%EC%8A%A4%20-%20%EC%A0%84%ED%99%94%EB%B2%88%ED%98%B8%20%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D(Hash%20Lv.2)/#%ED%92%80%EC%9D%B4\">풀이</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Algorithm/Programmers/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%A8%B8%EC%8A%A4%20-%20%EC%A0%84%ED%99%94%EB%B2%88%ED%98%B8%20%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D(Hash%20Lv.2)/#%EB%B0%B0%EC%9A%B4-%EA%B2%83\">배운 것</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"문제 확인 문제 설명 전화번호부에 적힌 전화번호 중, 한 번호가 다른 번호의 접두어인 경우가 있는지 확인하려 합니다.\n전화번호가 다음과 같을 경우, 구조대 전화번호는 영석이의 전화번호의 접두사입니다. 구조대 : 119 박준영 : 97 674 223 지영석 : 11 9552 4421 전화번호부에 적힌 전화번호를 담은 배열 phone_book 이 solution 함수의 매개변수로 주어질 때, 어떤 번호가 다른 번호의 접두어인 경우가 있으면 false를 그렇지 않으면 true를 return 하도록 s…","html":"<h2 id=\"문제-확인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"문제 확인 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 확인</h2>\n<details><summary>펼쳐보기</summary>\n<h3 id=\"문제-설명\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85\" aria-label=\"문제 설명 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 설명</h3>\n<p>전화번호부에 적힌 전화번호 중, 한 번호가 다른 번호의 접두어인 경우가 있는지 확인하려 합니다.\n전화번호가 다음과 같을 경우, 구조대 전화번호는 영석이의 전화번호의 접두사입니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>구조대 : 119</li>\n<li>박준영 : 97 674 223</li>\n<li>지영석 : 11 9552 4421</li>\n</ul>\n<p>전화번호부에 적힌 전화번호를 담은 배열 phone_book 이 solution 함수의 매개변수로 주어질 때, 어떤 번호가 다른 번호의 접두어인 경우가 있으면 false를 그렇지 않으면 true를 return 하도록 solution 함수를 작성해주세요.</p>\n<h3 id=\"제한-사항\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%9C-%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\" aria-label=\"제한 사항 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>제한 사항</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>phone_book의 길이는 1 이상 1,000,000 이하입니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>각 전화번호의 길이는 1 이상 20 이하입니다.</li>\n<li>같은 전화번호가 중복해서 들어있지 않습니다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"입출력-예제\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9E%85%EC%B6%9C%EB%A0%A5-%EC%98%88%EC%A0%9C\" aria-label=\"입출력 예제 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>입출력 예제</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>phone_book</th>\n<th>return</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>[“119”, “97674223”, “1195524421”]</td>\n<td>false</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>[“123”,“456”,“789”]</td>\n<td>true</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>[“12”,“123”,“1235”,“567”,“88”]</td>\n<td>false</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"입출력-예-설명\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9E%85%EC%B6%9C%EB%A0%A5-%EC%98%88-%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85\" aria-label=\"입출력 예 설명 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>입출력 예 설명</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>입출력 예 #1<br>\n앞에서 설명한 예와 같습다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>입출력 예 #2<br>\n한 번호가 다른 번호의 접두사인 경우가 없으므로, 답은 true입니다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>입출력 예 #3<br>\n첫 번째 전화번호, “12”가 두 번째 전화번호 “123”의 접두사입니다. 따라서 답은 false입니다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<p>알림</p>\n<p>2021년 3월 4일, 테스트 케이스가 변경되었습니다. 이로 인해 이전에 통과하던 코드가 더 이상 통과하지 않을 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"제공하는-소스-코드\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%9C%EA%B3%B5%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%86%8C%EC%8A%A4-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C\" aria-label=\"제공하는 소스 코드 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>제공하는 소스 코드</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    answer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">True</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> answer</code></pre></div>\n<p>출처 :\n<a href=\"https://programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/42577\">‘프로그래머스’</a></p>\n</details>\n<h2 id=\"접근\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%91%EA%B7%BC\" aria-label=\"접근 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>접근</h2>\n<p>각 문자열마다 모든 다른 문자열을 조회하는 방법은 최대한 피하려고 했다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>최악의 경우, O(N^2) 에 수렵하는 시간복잡도를 가질 것이기 때문에,<br>\n입력 배열의 길이 범위인 1 ~ 1,000,000 을 처리하기에는 조금 별로라고 생각했다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<br>\n<p>그래서, 해시 테이블을 활용하면서 반복 횟수를 최소한으로 줄이는 방법을 찾는데 초점을 뒀다.  </p>\n<p>바로, 모든 번호를 문자열의 인덱스만큼만 조회하도록 구성하는 방법이었다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>접두어와 접두어를 포함하는 단어는 앞에서부터는 무조건 같은 형태일테니,<br>\n첫 인덱스부터 공통되는 문자의 개수를 세면 접두어가 없는 경우를 가장 빠르게 찾는다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<br>\n<p>하지만, 코딩한 내용을 제출한 결과가 정확도 부분을 만족하지 못했고,<br>\n코드 수정을 몇 번 해보고는, 접근 방식에 문제가 있다는 것을 깨달았다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"검색\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B2%80%EC%83%89\" aria-label=\"검색 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>검색</h2>\n<p>문제를 검색 해보았고, 처리 방식은 맞았는데 구현 방식이 문제였다는 것을 확인했다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://velog.io/@vvakki_/%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%A8%B8%EC%8A%A4-%ED%95%B4%EC%8B%9C-%EC%A0%84%ED%99%94%EB%B2%88%ED%98%B8-%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D\">‘[프로그래머스] 해시 - 전화번호 목록 - Velog’</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<br>\n<p>정답 코드의 구성을 파악해보니, 동작 순서를 반대로 구현한 것이었다.</p>\n<details><summary>적용한 방법 : 인덱스 값을 늘려가면서 모든 문자열을 조회하는 방법</summary>\n<ul>\n<li>해당 문자열이 확실하게 접두어인지 검증하는 부분이 없다..<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">(뭔가 잘못됐음을 깨닫고 코딩을 멈춘 상태..)</code></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token triple-quoted-string string\">'''\n    input\n        - phone_book : [전화번호] (1 &lt;= [] &lt;= 1000000, 1 &lt;= i &lt;= 20)\n    output\n        - answer     : 임의의 번호가 다른 번호의 접두어인 경우의 진리값\n    result\n        - 정확성 : 62.5/100\n        - 효율성 : 12.5/100\n    '''</span>\n    table   <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">dict</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    index   <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n    maximum <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">len</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> key<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token builtin\">len</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">while</span> index <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> maximum<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        count <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">dict</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> number <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> number <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> table<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n                <span class=\"token keyword\">continue</span>\n            digit <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> number<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>index<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> digit <span class=\"token keyword\">not</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> count<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n                count<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>digit<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n            count<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>digit<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>count<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>values<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">True</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> number <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> number <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> table<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n                <span class=\"token keyword\">continue</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> count<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>index<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">and</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">len</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> index<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n                <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">False</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> count<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>index<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">or</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">len</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> index<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n                table<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n\n        index <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span></code></pre></div>\n</details>\n<details><summary>올바른 방법 : 모든 문자열을 첫 문자부터 더해가면서, 해시 테이블에 존재하는지 확인하는 방법</summary>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token triple-quoted-string string\">'''\n    input\n        - phone_book : [전화번호] (1 &lt;= [] &lt;= 1000000, 1 &lt;= i &lt;= 20)\n    output\n        - answer     : 임의의 번호가 다른 번호의 접두어인 경우의 진리값\n    result\n        - 정확성 : 100/100\n        - 효율성 : 100/100\n    '''</span>\n    answer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">True</span>\n    hash_map <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> phone_number <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        hash_map<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>phone_number<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> phone_number <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        temp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> number <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> phone_number<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            temp <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> number\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> temp <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> hash_map <span class=\"token keyword\">and</span> temp <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> phone_number<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n                answer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">False</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> answer</code></pre></div>\n</details>\n<br>\n<details><summary>두 풀이 방식의 결과 비교하기</summary>\n<ul>\n<li>왼쪽(내 풀이) 은 평균적으로 메모리를 적게 사용했고, 일부 효율성 테스트에서는 더 좋은 성능을 보였다.<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">(접두어가 없는 경우엔 즉시 반환하기 때문인 것 같다.)</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 76.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"results\"\n        title=\"results\"\n        src=\"/static/33ae2b365ff003f707b13da839421e39/0b533/results.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/33ae2b365ff003f707b13da839421e39/5a46d/results.png 300w,\n/static/33ae2b365ff003f707b13da839421e39/0b533/results.png 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n</details>\n<h2 id=\"풀이\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%92%80%EC%9D%B4\" aria-label=\"풀이 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>풀이</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>올바른 풀이를 기준으로 작성했다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<details><summary>1. 전화번호들을 저장할 해시 테이블을 생성한다.</summary>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    answer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">True</span>\n    hash_map <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> answer</code></pre></div>\n</details>\n<details><summary>2. 각 전화번호를 해시 테이블의 key 로 입력한다.</summary>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    answer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">True</span>\n    hash_map <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> phone_number <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        hash_map<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>phone_number<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> answer</code></pre></div>\n</details>\n<details><summary>3. 전화번호부를 순회하는 반복문를 생성하고, 임시 접두어 변수를 선언한다.</summary>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    answer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">True</span>\n    hash_map <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> phone_number <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        hash_map<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>phone_number<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> phone_number <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        temp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> answer</code></pre></div>\n</details>\n<details><summary>4. 전화번호를 하나씩 더해, 가능한 접두어를 모두 구성하도록 반복문을 추가한다.</summary>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    answer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">True</span>\n    hash_map <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> phone_number <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        hash_map<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>phone_number<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> phone_number <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        temp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> number <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> phone_number<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            temp <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> number\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> answer</code></pre></div>\n</details>\n<details><summary>5. 임시 접두어 변수가 해시 테이블에 있는지 조회한다.</summary>\n<ul>\n<li>이 때, 현재의 전화번호와 조회하는 접두어가 일치하지 않도록 조건을 추가한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    answer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">True</span>\n    hash_map <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> phone_number <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        hash_map<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>phone_number<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> phone_number <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> phone_book<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        temp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> number <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> phone_number<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            temp <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> number\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> temp <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> hash_map <span class=\"token keyword\">and</span> temp <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> phone_number<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n                answer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">False</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> answer</code></pre></div>\n</details>\n<h2 id=\"배운-것\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%B0%EC%9A%B4-%EA%B2%83\" aria-label=\"배운 것 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>배운 것</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>자신의 의도를 올바르게 코드로 옮기는 능력을 기를 필요가 있다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>여러 문제를 풀어보면서, 감을 익혀야겠다.</li>\n<li>구현하려는 기능을 정리하는 방법에 대해 연구해봐야겠다..</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Python 에서 딕셔너리를 선언하는 방법에는 성능 차이가 있다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>처음 알게된 사실이었고, 공학 수업을 듣고있는 터라 뭔가 더 와닿았다.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/17097985/dict-vs-in-python-which-is-better/17098017\">‘스택오버플로 - dict() vs {}’</a>\n에서 내용을 확인할 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>해시 테이블과 해시 맵의 차이점을 알게됐다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Java 기준으로, 동기화 지원 여부의 차이가 있다고 한다.</li>\n<li>해시 테이블은 Null 값을 허용하지 않고, 병렬 처리(동기화) 가 필요할 때 사용한다.</li>\n<li>반대로, 해시 맵은 NUll 값을 허용하고, 병렬 처리를 고려하지 않을 때 사용한다.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://hee96-story.tistory.com/48\">‘[자료구조] Hash/HashTable/HashMap - Hee’s story’</a> 참고</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>다른 사람의 풀이를 보고 zip() 함수와 startswith() 메서드의 사용법을 알게됐다.</li>\n</ul>\n<details><summary>해시를 사용하지 않은 풀이 방법</summary>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">(Python 에서 camelCase 라니; 불-편..)</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>phoneBook<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    phoneBook <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">sorted</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>phoneBook<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> p1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> p2 <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">zip</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>phoneBook<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> phoneBook<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> p2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>startswith<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>p1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">False</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">True</span></code></pre></div>\n</details>\n<details><summary>zip 함수는 반복 가능한 객체(iterable) 를 인자로 받아, 컨테이너 구조의 zip 객체를 반환한다.</summary>\n<ul>\n<li>여러 개의 인자를 받을 수 있으며, 입력받은 모든 객체의 정보를 순서대로 묶어 반환한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token builtin\">zip</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token builtin\">zip</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">object</span> at <span class=\"token number\">0x7ff80a3190a0</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">zip</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> a\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token builtin\">zip</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">object</span> at <span class=\"token number\">0x7ff80a319690</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token builtin\">list</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n</details>\n<details><summary>startswith 메서드는 문자열 정보에서만 지원되고, 진리 값을 반환한다.</summary>\n<ul>\n<li>해당 문자열이 인자로 받은 문자열로 시작되는지 여부를 탐색하고, 그 결과를 반환한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<details><summary>첫 번째 인자로는 문자열, 혹은 문자열로만 구성된 튜플 자료형만 입력받을 수 있다.</summary>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> test <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'haha'</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> test<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>startswith<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nTraceback <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>most recent call last<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  File <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;stdin>\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> line <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>module<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\nTypeError<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> startswith first arg must be <span class=\"token builtin\">str</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">or</span> a <span class=\"token builtin\">tuple</span> of <span class=\"token builtin\">str</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">not</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">int</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> test<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>startswith<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nTraceback <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>most recent call last<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  File <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;stdin>\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> line <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>module<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\nTypeError<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> startswith first arg must be <span class=\"token builtin\">str</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">or</span> a <span class=\"token builtin\">tuple</span> of <span class=\"token builtin\">str</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">not</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">float</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> test<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>startswith<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nTraceback <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>most recent call last<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  File <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;stdin>\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> line <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>module<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\nTypeError<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> startswith first arg must be <span class=\"token builtin\">str</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">or</span> a <span class=\"token builtin\">tuple</span> of <span class=\"token builtin\">str</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">not</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">list</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> test<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>startswith<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nTraceback <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>most recent call last<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  File <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;stdin>\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> line <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>module<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\nTypeError<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> startswith first arg must be <span class=\"token builtin\">str</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">or</span> a <span class=\"token builtin\">tuple</span> of <span class=\"token builtin\">str</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">not</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">dict</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> test<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>startswith<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token boolean\">False</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> test<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>startswith<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'ha'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token boolean\">True</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> test<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>startswith<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'h'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token boolean\">True</span></code></pre></div>\n</details>\n<details><summary>2, 3번째 인자를 통해 탐색 범위를 지정할 수 있다.</summary>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Parameter</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>value</td>\n<td>Required. The value to check if the string starts with</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>start</td>\n<td>Optional. An Integer specifying at which position to start the search</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>end</td>\n<td>Optional. An Integer specifying at which position to end the search</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>- 출처 :\n<a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/python/ref_string_startswith.asp\">‘w3schools.com’</a></p>\n</details>\n</details>\n<br>\n<ul>\n<li>20210404 - 마크다운 구성 변경</li>\n<li>20210418 - 표기 수정(2번째, 3번째 -> 2, 3번째)</li>\n<li>20220418 - 표기 수정(접근법 -> 처리 방식, 메소드 -> 메서드)</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"프로그래머스 - 전화번호 목록(Hash Lv.2)","tags":["Algorithm","Programmers","Hash","Lv.2","wecode","위코드"],"date":"March 07, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Algorithm/Programmers/프로그래머스 - 전화번호 목록(Hash Lv.2)/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Experience Storage/TIL/2021/03/01~07/2021030